{"tid":1260953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"身為愛國愛港市民，我地七一熱烈慶祝回歸祖國 #yup#","createTime":"2019-06-27T04:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T11:40:18.000Z","uid":5843,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28cdb263c7b0733f7eccea3d3ccd8ce86e873c82","tid":1260953,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/upzjaCf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FupzjaCf.jpg&h=323e4bed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《🎊七一熱烈慶祝回歸祖國🎉》<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n幫手廣傳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n活動目標 1.表達四大訴求 2.不舉  3.以多國語言與國歌和音<br />\n<br />\n活動當日<br />\n1. 1/7 6:30金紫荊廣傳集合，(而<br />\n30/6既2200左右開始後金紫荊廣場集合，為霸頭位開始做好準備，唔係排頭位睇表演都拉下話？)<br />\n<br />\n2. 等待期間派發歌詞，教人用ampme，用聖詩做rehearsal，當宗教活動，如果有樂器組仲可以一齊練定，有成10個鐘練（印埋國歌樂譜大條道理話聲援做掩護），等佢地趕我地唔走，要佢地22年來第一次不舉 <br />\n<br />\n3. 萬一清場，由佢清，反正佢一定要留個位置俾觀眾，不舉唔成我都有plan b，用多國語言與國歌和音，萬人合唱（試問誰還未發聲 - 暫決），唱到電視台都錄到<br />\n<br />\n4. 唱完基本上可以散，因為我地已經達到目的，傳媒有收音就一定可以聽到，睇下tvb敢唔敢播，唔好諗住開演唱會，做多就好容易錯多less is more<br />\n<br />\n重點 ※最後嗌多次五大訴求※   事成散水<br />\n<br />\n訴求為先<br />\n騎劫次要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1/7塞爆金紫荊公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/freedumbcunt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreedumbcunt&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=e00ce02d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/freedumbcunt</a><br />\n<br />\n自由hi 屌傻hi 頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/diu9gov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdiu9gov&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=bd76cde1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/diu9gov</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/71dyhtps?igshid=1l1betojmh4mc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2F71dyhtps%3Figshid%3D1l1betojmh4mc&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=89cebd81\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/71dyhtps?igshid=1l1betojmh4mc</a></span>"},{"pid":"8d1f899bc2c75e2fe7e982cd3b6a056a7d427f88","tid":1260953,"uid":69301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"個兩個負皮嘅係咪無睇正文，比個標題嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ab6740d620041a38b396d9f536b25b9a69a33f","tid":1260953,"uid":237888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d1f899bc2c75e2fe7e982cd3b6a056a7d427f88","tid":1260953,"uid":69301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"個兩個負皮嘅係咪無睇正文，比個標題嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"應該係因為偷文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076a1f70ae47fa7ee8e7a7cd43f2e4fd44ed10db","tid":1260953,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53ab6740d620041a38b396d9f536b25b9a69a33f","tid":1260953,"uid":237888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d1f899bc2c75e2fe7e982cd3b6a056a7d427f88","tid":1260953,"uid":69301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"個兩個負皮嘅係咪無睇正文，比個標題嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"應該係因為偷文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}